changes from 0.3.0 to 0.4.0:

Rds <rds@rdsarts.com>

	* Added: nb_of_fans routine
	* Changed: Made the percent() routine use try/except 
	* Added: some complexity to test.py.

	
changes from 0.2.0 to 0.3.0:

2003-12-15 Rds <rds@rdsarts.com>

	* added: support for Linux kernel 2.6.
	
2003-12-14 Tilo Riemer <riemer@lincvs.org>
	
	* fixed: estimated_lifetime returns always
	a real number now instead of strings like
	charging.
	NOTE: the return type has changed from
	string to float

	
